title: Vlajkovic - Military secret 1&2 (2004) (banned in Serbia).zip
description: This is the english translation of Vladan Vlajkovic&#039;s explosive book Military secret (originally Vojna tajna) (2004) which in 2 parts documents some of the most secret arrangements which occured in Serbia under the rule of Slobodan Milosevic. Among other unique information it contains transcripts of secret meetings of Serbia&#039;s high military command and its analysis. Vlajkovic is Serbia&#039;s military intelligence officer and has been imprisoned for releasing this documents and his book banned in Serbia. More than 400 pages of interesting reading. A must read for everyone.
